Build Container Incident Response Workflow with Sysdig + ELK
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Deploy and configure Sysdig Falco for container runtime security monitoring
Set up ELK stack (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana) for centralized log analysis
Create automated incident response workflows using container security events
Build comprehensive dashboards for container security monitoring
Implement alerting mechanisms for container security incidents
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of Linux command line
Familiarity with Docker containers
Knowledge of YAML configuration files
Understanding of log analysis concepts
